 <p class="mt-2 text-sm text-ash">Master-planned community build-out — Cadence, Inspirada, Skye Canyon.</p>
 </a>
 <a href="/service-areas/spring-valley/" class="group border border-hairline bg-panel p-6 transition-colors hover:border-gold-500">
 <h3 class="font-heading text-lg font-bold uppercase tracking-tight text-charcoal group-hover:text-gold-600">Spring Valley</h3>
 <p class="mt-2 text-sm text-ash">Service-trade dense — HVAC, plumbing, electrical residential and commercial.</p>
 </a>
 <a href="/service-areas/boulder-city/" class="group border border-hairline bg-panel p-6 transition-colors hover:border-gold-500">
